October dealsI have allocation exceptions that require a deal to be extended Meter Tenaska is showing small volumes flowed on days there was no deal Can you extend the deal throughout the month so that the volumes will have a deal to link to I have the same situation on meter If you have any questions please let me know Thanks Susan
